originalText.text: I recently enlisted Homey Cleaners for a comprehensive cleaning as I moved into my new apartment and was exceptionally pleased with their service. Their team was outstanding in their communication, always keeping me in the loop and eagerly responding to the particularities of my cleaning needs. They went above and beyond to accommodate my requests, taking detailed photos to show their progress—a gesture I greatly appreciated. Although the price was a bit steep, the level of thoroughness and quality of cleaning provided by Homey Cleaners was absolutely worth it. They came prepared with all the necessary supplies, which made the entire process seamless. I would undoubtedly recommend Homey Cleaners to anyone looking for top-notch cleaning services.

originalText.text: Excellent work! the amount of hard work that the team did was awesome. They took all day as the apartment needed pretty deep cleaning. I cannot be more thankful for the Homey team to make my apartment a clean home again and taking the time to do so. They are very prompt and responsive. I would recommend everyone, you don’t know what you are missing until you have a super clean apartment.

originalText.text:
I ordered a deep clean via Homey, and from ordering to the clean itself, I was very impressed at the attention to detail. Homey was very responsive to all the parameters of the deep clean I needed, and gave me a detailed breakdown of the costs for my specific apartment so nothing would be unexpected. They were very accommodating, even as I had multiple questions about what they could clean.

The actual clean itself was very impressive! The landlord was there to drop by, and they were really satisfied with the quality of work and cleanliness. What really impressed me was how neatened up everything was; every surface was cleaned (which is totally expected from a deep clean!) but they took the time to actually organize all our belongings in a way that was presentable.

All this is to say that I'm very happy with the detailed work here. Thank you, Homey!

originalText.text: Yaleny and Margot did a fantastic job of cleaning my apartment, they worked hard and got all the nooks and crannies that I've been neglecting---my mom died recently and I haven't had the energy to clean. They even got stains off one of my tea kettles that I thought were permanent---I thought I'd tried everything---no idea how they achieved such a miracle. They were polite, friendly, and efficient.

originalText.text: I've had two separate cleanings by Homey over the summer and will be reaching out going forward for maintaining my apartment. The first cleaning was a deep clean and the second cleaning was a general cleaning after several months. Both times, I came back to a spotless apartment. I highly recommend Homey for their professionalism, quality of service, and efficiency.
